<plot>A family is torn apart when their "good" boy Charlie decides to turn bad. He is arrested and given a bail of $500,000. Only one relative, martial arts instructor and psychologist, Uncle Kenneth has that kind of wealth; but will he put everything he has on the line for his nephew? Would you? After much pressure he does. A short while later, Charlie decides to skip town. His uncle loses everything but will not rest unless he captures Charlie and brings him back to justice himself.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?220271</url></doc>
